message.content: Though your wings and your scars are new, you may join us,' 'I am Lily-yo. We three are humans. You are only flymen. We will not join you.' The Captives grunted in boredom. The Chief Captive spoke again. 'Always this talk from you of the Heavy World! You have joined us. You are flymen, we are human. You know little, we know much.'
